#~ "ottenuto il pacchetto base di &kmymoney;."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you have installed from RPM, the OFX Importer Plugin is contained "
#~ "within the kmymoney-ofx package. It should be available from whatever "
#~ "source you got the base &kmymoney; package. If you have built from "
#~ "sources, all you need to do is have preferably the libOFX 0.9 development "
#~ "headers and libraries installed on your system. The &kmymoney; build "
#~ "process will detect these and compile the plugin. At the time of release "
#~ "of &kmymoney; 4.6, the latest libofx version was 0.9.4, which is also the "
